  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Sega Rally makes its debut on the handheld format with this GBA rendition. Choose from a number of fully licensed rally cars (Subaru, Ford, Toyota, Mitsubishi, etc.) and hit the rally tracks.\n\nYou'll find a number of different terrains, from dirt to snow, country roads to jungle hills. The aim is to cross the finish line with the best time possible, beating out the opposition to the main prize. You'll have the chance to upgrade and repair your car as you go, which is important if you want to find the reach the line first. The more you win, the more you'll unlock. From new cars and tracks to mini-games and galleries.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ]
